---
description: CI/CD pipeline and deployment best practices for automated and secure software delivery.
alwaysApply: false
---

- All code must pass linting and formatting checks before merging.
- All code must be automatically deployed to a staging environment before production.
- All pull requests must be reviewed by at least one other developer.
- Enforce branch protection rules on main/master.
- Automatically run security checks (e.g., Snyk, Dependabot) on all dependencies.
